Definition: a measuring system that detects and locates objects on the same principle as radar but uses light from a laser
Example: a potential technology for detecting air turbulence that can affect aircraft
Synonyms: measuring_instrument, a, measuring, system, that, detects, and, locates, objects, on, the, same, principle, as, radar, but, uses, light, from, laser, potential, technology, for, detecting, air, turbulence, can, affect, aircraft
Category: noun.artifact
